data.description: Welcome to the gated community of Picket Fences, centrally located between Marine Corps Air Station, Marine Corps Recruit Depot Paris Island & Naval Hospital Beaufort. Downtown Beaufort is only a 15 minute drive away. This 4 bed 3 bath corner lot home was built in 2016. On the 1st floor are the main suite w/ spacious bathroom & 2 bedrooms that share a bathroom. Upstairs is an additional bedroom w/ full bathroom. The kitchen is open to the family room & has a separate dining area w/ spacious island for additional seating. Picket Fences is an active & walkable community that has a pool, playground, walking trails & dock to enjoy the water.
